
Ranger Help for: enemy rodent
=============================

SUMMARY:
Choosing rodent means your Ranger specializes against rats, mice, beavers,
porcupines, giant rodents, and other gnawing creatures.

This is a practical choice in forests, plains, swamps, deserts, caves,
beaches, and cold lands where small pests become real threats.

COMMAND:
  setenemy rodent

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
